Additionally, the entrances to Hell branches are guarded by monsters from these Hells:
*Cocytus: [[ice statue]]s, [[water elemental]]s, [[simulacrum (monster)|simulacrums]], [[skeleton (monster)|skeletons]], and [[zombie]]s.
*The Iron City of Dis: [[iron troll]]s, [[war gargoyle]]s, [[iron golem]]s and [[iron dragon]]s.
*Gehenna: [[fire elemental]]s, [[molten gargoyle]]s.
*Tartarus: [[skeletal warrior]]s, [[ancient champion]]s, [[shadow dragon]]s, [[lich]]es, and [[shadow wraith]]s.

