'''Sumoned by Geryon'''
*{{monsterlink|Hell beast}}

==History==
Prior to [[0.14]], it was necessary to kill [[Geryon]] and sound his [[Horn of Geryon|horn]] to open up the entrances to the four main branches of Hell, and all portals to the Vestibule were closed when you picked up the Orb.

